data.description: Tallmadge Twp 3 bed 2 bath home with classic charm, solid roof, newer windows, and a new furnace and air system. The 2-stall garage adds practicality. The location blends with accessibility offering easy access to amenities.  Inside, the living area kitchen dining and living room on the main plus a bedroom with connected bath.  There is also enclosed porches on the front and rear of the home.  Hardwood floors in most of the home. 2 bedrooms and full bath up, This one is ready for your personal touch.  Easy to view
